These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, metal, funk, pop, rock
6 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, fish, goat, pony, horse
 1. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 3. the fan of pop is not the owner of the pony##6
 4. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
 5. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
 6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
 7. the owner of the pony is not the fan of gospel##6
 8. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of electronic is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the fan of funk##7
10. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
12. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
13. the owner of the frog is the fan of electronic##1
14. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
15. the fan of rock is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | electronic | metal   | rock     | gospel    | pop   |
| Pet           | pony | frog   | horse | goat | fish | lizard |

