.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, western, scientific, comedy, adventure
6 different pets are kept: horse, pony, ferret, cat, goat, bird
 1. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 7. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching comedy movies is not the owner of the goat##6
10. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the cat##7
11. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
14. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
15. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
16. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
17. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the person watching comedy movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | adventure | scientific | comedy     | western      | mystery |
| Pet           | pony         | ferret        | goat   | cat | horse | bird    |

