.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, juice, fanta, sprite, iced-tea
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: cricket, skateboarding, weightlifting, skiing, biathlon, volleyball
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 2. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person drinking fanta##6
 5. the person drinking milk is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 9. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking 7up##7
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
13. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
14. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | sprite        | fanta | iced-tea    | milk    | juice | 7up |
| Sport      | skateboarding | biathlon  | volleyball | skiing | cricket | weightlifting      |

