 6. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 7. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking coffee##7
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking milk##7
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
13. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking milk##1
14. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

