11. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the person driving the bike##7
13. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | hamster   | hedgehog | snake      | ferret | fish  | cat   |
| Transport   | bus | ship  | bike | helicopter   | airplane | van |

