.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: cooking, chess, reading, board-games, filmmaking, baking
The people have 6 different jobs:  bartender, designer, photographer, security-guard, librarian, analyst
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the photographer##5
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the security-guard and the designer##7
 5. the analyst is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is the librarian##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
 8. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
10. the designer is somewhere to the right of the analyst##5
11. the analyst is on the right of the photographer##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the security-guard##5
13. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is reading##7
14. the designer is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
15. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | reading         | board-games | chess | cooking   | baking | filmmaking  |
| Job     | librarian | security-guard  | photographer  | analyst | designer  | bartender |

 